01:29:12.746 --> 01:29:15.791
<i>Ne vjerujem.
To je Cruz Ramirez za pobjedu!</i>

01:29:15.958 --> 01:29:17.292
<i>Bez riječi sam!</i>

01:29:19.084 --> 01:29:21.754
Lijep završetak, Cruz! Ti si to učinila!

01:29:22.129 --> 01:29:24.006
Cruz Ramirez!

01:29:24.256 --> 01:29:26.342
- Da, ideš!
- Tako treba, Cruz!

01:29:27.009 --> 01:29:28.052
